*Index: amount of antimicrobials (grs)/ (harvest (ton) + mortality (ton))
**Harvest: data on tons received at the plant, obtained from traceability.
***Dead biomass: calculation obtained from the sum of the number of dead fish in each cage
by the respective average weight, according to the information declared in SIFA.
